    "description": "<p><em>TKNP</em> International in Singapore is the founding member of the network of <em>TKNP</em>International member firms, which provides Audit, Tax and Advisory services in eight principal cities across the Asia-Pacific region.</p>\n<p>With a history in Singapore dating back to 1971, TKNP International has a track record of 50 years in providing trusted and reliable professional services to businesses within Asia and beyond.</p>\n<p><em>TKNP</em> International member firms are located strategically in locations across Asia. Our regional network of independent member firms includes Australia, Hong Kong, India, Indonesia, Malaysia, Philippines, Singapore and South Korea. We are also represented in major cities worldwide.</p>\n<p><em>www.tknpinternational.com</em></p>",
